{"tid":2491107,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西九龍法院外男子與建制人士口角 警按頭埋牆 被指「口水襲警」被捕","createTime":"2021-04-16T05:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T05:45:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"010c0058c170462440e9d177a6ae35e9825a59b5","tid":2491107,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"西九龍裁判法院今早處理 8.18 維園集會案求情，大批市民到場聲援，另有親建制團體到場示威。中午 12 時半左右，在法院對面馬路，一名男子被警員截查，然後帶上警車。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，男子沒有佩戴口罩，起初與親建制派人士口角，其後親建制派人士在警員保護下帶走。警員則截查該名男子。<br />\n<br />\n截查期間，男子多次高呼「警察打人」，警員拉起封鎖線，阻隔傳媒拍攝。警員要求該名男子戴回口罩，惟男子表明「我唔戴，我就係要俾人影到」，警員將他頭部按在牆上，並指他「口水襲警」，男子隨後被帶上警車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/4079763665442556\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F4079763665442556&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLX%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=8892fc77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/4079763665442556</a>"},{"pid":"c716f0c335ea58cfc7c0d6baee38d01f8bed2bb5","tid":2491107,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5102b15a5aeedac879df81993e1d5159f69d4b2f","tid":2491107,"uid":170949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"686787255342f3f44bca9c1f1dff8b1d15e7d927","tid":2491107,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"口水襲警"}]}